s perfect and we all make mistakes, but not all of us admit to mistakes made.', 15050, 0), (158215, 'Focus on making yourself better, not thinking you are better.', 1168, 0), (158216, 'The good don''t masquerade their goodness, they just are.', 15050, 0), (158217, 'It''s not hard to create self-beliefs that produce a successful and happy life. The main job is to unlearn your limiting beliefs.', 26483, 0), (158218, 'The key to sticking with any diet is learning how to control hunger and manage cravings.', 23226, 0), (158219, 'What inspires you to do what you do is the reason why you persist, even in the face of trouble.', 15050, 0), (158220, 'You can''t improve anything if you don''t first know what needs to be improved.', 1168, 0), (158221, 'If you emit positive energy, even people who don''t like you will not be negative when around you.', 15050, 0), (158222, 'You have only 3 days-yesterday is won or lost-today is just with you.Tomorrow you have not.Act now, unlock your potentials', 8543, 0), (158223, 'In the long run most short cuts are flawed - especially on journeys to ''so-called'' success', 4889, 0), (158224, 'If you are humble enough to admit to your flaws then you are capable of correcting them.', 15050, 0), (158225, 'Not many abilities are inherent. Most are acquired through patient practice, and those that are inherent are enhanced and utilized through practice too.', 15050, 0), (158226, 'You MUST know You to do YOU!', 29707, 0), (158227, 'Persistence is key when you want to achieve. You can''t afford to quit just because you don''t feel good about failure.', 15050, 0), (158228, 'The joy of success outweighs whatever negativity you might get from failing a couple of times.', 15050, 0), (158229, 'One of the most liberating things a person can do is to admit that he or she is human and is flawed.', 15050, 0), (158230, 'Like David: Let not your age limit what God can do. Go confront the Goliaths of life.', 8543, 0), (158231, 'What they say doesn''t matter because it can be lies, but it''s what they do that matters because it always speaks truth.', 15050, 0), (158232, 'Everyone is entitled to an opinion, but it doesn''t mean that they are right and you should listen to them.', 15050, 0), (158233, 'Do not blindly accept anyone''s definition of your life and define it yourself.', 15050, 0), (158234, 'Success comes from the inside out. In order to change what is on the outside, you must first change what is on the inside.', 11345, 0), (158235, 'You just can''t let life happen to you, you have to make life happen.', 11345, 0), (158236, 'Everybody has somebody. It could be a friend, a lover, a spouse, a writing partner, or even That One Person You See At The Coffee Shop each day. Sometimes they exist to comfort you. Sometimes they exist to drive you absolutely mad. Be open to either as a form of self-improvement.', 195, 0), (158237, 'You''ve just got to take a good hard look at yourself, change what needs to be changed, and move on.', 1051, 0), (158238, 'You''re either growing or dying. Stagnation does not exist in the universe.', 29708, 0), (158239, 'Develop the wings of loyalty and you will fly above the dooms of disappointments. Disloyalty has one whistle; when it’s blown, opportunities take to their heels!', 3301, 0), (158240, 'What I’m starting to realize is that when you conform, people are not accepting you for who you are. They’re accepting you for who they think you are.', 22627, 0), (158241, 'Learn to say no, know when to say yes, and use the words ‘I choose.’ It is the key that will open you to limitless manifestation of your beingness.', 14568, 0), (158242, 'Keep working on yourself', 29709, 0), (158243, 'Average people have a world view that says being comfortable with who and where they are in life is the key to happiness. The great ones have a world view that says happiness is learning, growing and becoming.', 29708, 0), (158244, 'What I’ve always insisted on from myself is to do as well as I could, and keep doing better until I’m at least competent. Long ago I learned that to achieve anything, one must start where one stands. Or spend eternity waiting for the right moment. Which never comes.', 23704, 0), (158245, 'If thousand people say you can''t, and you alone believe you can, you will make it happen! But if million people say you can, and you alone believe you can''t, you can''t make it happen. It all depends on you!', 3301, 0), (158246, 'Creating Identity', 22612, 0), (158247, 'It''s all about how you feel, not how you look', 6058, 0), (158248, 'Everybody must be given the opportunity for self liberation and development.', 2878, 0), (158249, 'Two basic principles', 29710, 0), (158250, 'I have come to terms with the reality this life may not bring another romantically to share this journey with me. I do this not just for me, but for everyone who spends their life seeking and wishing. When we are wishing, we are missing.', 29711, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (158251, 'In discovery- driven planning, learning is the essential unit of progress. A course correction isn’t equivalent to failure, it’s an opportunity to re-calibrate so you can move more quickly up the learning curve.', 29712, 0), (158252, 'Adversity relieves people of vanity and egotism. It discourages selfishness by proving that no one can succeed without the cooperation of others.', 1187, 0), (158253, 'Caleb told me that our mother said there was evil in everyone, and the first step to loving someone else is to recognize that evil in ourselves, so we can forgive them.', 73, 0), (158254, 'Remember who you are by Gods divine plan and strive to fit into his divine pattern.', 8543, 0), (158255, 'Blame is such a self-defeating choice. It renders one helpless, putting any solution well out of reach, for we rarely can change others. Consider this, a solution well within your reach, someone you can surely change: Yourself.', 29713, 0), (158256, 'Self discovery is the best investment that you can make.', 29714, 0), (158257, 'About potentials, ,decipher(decode),discern, decide and determine what they are', 8543, 0), (158258, 'No matter how rich, powerful or handsome he is, he is defenseless against your womanly power.', 29706, 0), (158259, 'It has always been simple, but making it hard was always your way of avoiding pain. If you want to change your life, you have to change what you are doing. It wasn''t his fault, her fault, their fault or the circumstances. It was your inability to choose. So, life chose for you. Somewhere in that crazy mind of yours time stopped. You thought someone would rescue you, but they didn''t. You have to rescue yourself. This is not a fire you can put out; you have to walk through it, in order to reach life. Getting burned is apart of growth, didn''t you know?', 290, 0), (158260, 'To have a different life you have be a different person. You have to do what you haven''t done. You have to become the person that fits that dream. But most of all, you have to realize that if you don''t step into your story it becomes the moral of the story. Your inaction is a lesson you leave to your kids-- I was too afraid to change.', 290, 0), (158261, 'Getting hold of the difficulty deep down is what is hard. Because if it is grasped near the surface it simply remains the difficulty it was. It has to be pulled out by the roots; and that involves our beginning to think about these things in a new way. The change is as decisive as, for example, that from the alchemical to the chemical way of thinking. The new way of thinking is what is so hard to establish. Once the new way of thinking has been established, the old problems vanish; indeed they become hard to recapture. For they go with our way of expressing ourselves and, if we clothe ourselves in a new form of expression, the old problems are discarded along with the old garment.', 1163, 0), (158262, 'It is good to know; it is better to do; it is best to be. To be pure and strong, to be honest and earnest, to be kindly and thoughtful, and in all to be true,...', 27143, 0), (158263, 'Before you go out and occupy Wall Street, occupy your own brain!', 5687, 0), (158264, 'Even the top motivational speakers and inspirational writers are constantly reading books from other self-improvement people, because they truly understand that knowledge has no limit to it.', 166, 0), (158265, 'Men who pride themselves on being shrewd in discovering the weak points, the vanity, the dishonesty, immorality, intrigue, and pettiness of others think they understand character. They know only a part of character. They know only the depths to which some men may sink; they know not the heights to which some men may rise.', 21688, 0), (158266, 'It is not how many times we get lost, but how many times we seek the path, again and again, that determines our level of consciousness.', 5084, 0), (158267, 'You can turn your anger into positive energy and do good things that will turn your life around', 29715, 0), (158268, 'I try not to let other people''s problems problem me.', 18341, 0), (158269, 'Generally speaking, we are w-a-y too hard on ourselves! I used to place enough pressure on myself to crush an elephant!', 29716, 0), (158270, 'Opportunities present themselves only to the patient, man and beast, and only they take advantage of those opportunities.', 29717, 0), (158271, 'If you Don''t where you going, look back and see where you have come from', 29718, 0), (158272, 'Self-change can only come after self-understanding.', 29719, 0), (158273, 'Paradise Is The Absolute Self~Respect.', 29720, 0), (158274, 'Being afraid does not define your character, but what you do in the face of fear does.', 29719, 0), (158275, 'We underestimate the power of our own mind – for both good and bad. If we can learn to control our mindset and our responses to the adverse things in our lives, we can absolutely control our own destiny.', 29719, 0), (158276, 'Learn to control the conversation you have with yourself and you will be unstoppable in your pursuits.', 29719, 0), (158277, 'We are not defined by the adversities in our lives, we are defined by how we manage them.', 29719, 0), (158278, 'Master thyself, seek to know thy soul.', 2878, 0), (158279, 'The habit of upgrading your mind with self-development messages is highly important, if you desire to reach the pinnacle of your true destiny in life.', 166, 0), (158280, '2.	Evolve and Be God: As we invoke the presence of Source, holding the focus through our mantras, we are drawing more and more proximity to the object of worship and gradually, we attain all the attributes we are invoking, i.e., we slowly evolve to be Angelic, invoking the presence of God/Source.', 6127, 0), (158281, 'I thought you might appreciate this.....“Excerpt from my lecture Sunday February 22, 2015 at Soul-Esteem Center10 Commandments - God knew when he gave us choice some would make the wrong choices, but God wanted his creation, man, to have free will and felt later it necessary to write the 10 Commandants as a reminder of how God wanted his creations to perform. The 10 Commandants contain 5 positives and five negatives”― I. Alan Appt, The Strength in Knowingtags: motivational, philosophy, psychology, self-helpPeace to all,Alan Appt', 28979, 0), (158282, 'Never invest in any kind of relationship with anyone who is not willing to work on themselves just a little every day. A person who takes no interest in any form of self-improvement, personal development or spiritual growth will also not be inclined to make much of an effort building a truly meaningful connection with you. A relationship with only one partner willing to do the work ceases to be a relationship. And as anyone who has been there will tell you - it''s pointless to try and dance the tango solo.', 4659, 0), (158283, 'Blame doesn''t empower you. It keeps you stuck in a place you don''t want to be because you don''t want to make the temporary, but painful decision, to be responsible for the outcome of your own life''s happiness.', 290, 0), (158284, 'We all must deal with our shadows the best we can. No one can conquer them for us.', 29721, 0), (158285, 'When our thoughts, at times, wander into darkness... remember we are human and have been imbued with free will to choose the light.', 11993, 0), (158286, 'Budgeting has only one rule: Do not go over budget.', 29722, 0), (158287, 'The biggest gift to oneself is affording yourself a chance to learn.', 9273, 0), (158288, 'Discovering passion and purpose requires figuring out what works and what doesn''t. Mature, successful people establish their on rules. These rules are measured by only one standard: do they work?', 29723, 0), (158289, 'Life is not something that happens to us, Life happens through us.', 14553, 0), (158290, 'The major events in our lives receive the entire spotlight, but ultimately your life will be defined by the same handful of choices 